# Routing

- File-based routes in `src/routes/` — thin wiring only, no business logic.
- Export `Route` via `createFileRoute()` or `createRootRoute()`.
- Page components live in `src/pages/` or are composed from `@features/*`.
- `src/routeTree.gen.ts` is auto-generated — never edit manually.
- URL/search state belongs in route search params, not Effect Atoms.
